{
  "stem": "13483.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, because they were getting all the ships together, aligning them, putting them in their correct echelons.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I mean, there was over 3,000 ships, 5,000 ships.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the time, they lined up all the ships and gave you a signal to [INAUDIBLE], literally, in mid-English Channel for a few days, or two days.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we landed, or during?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had two storms, which were very, very bad.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I thought, one time, they'd have to turn us back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know where we were going to.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't know what part of France we were going to.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Could have been Calais.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Could have been anywhere.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Once we were-- I think around about the 5th of June did our commanding officers tell us where we were landing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because they gave us booklets to have to speak French and things like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Twiddling your thumbs.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You were under a lot of tension.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You knew-- I mean, we knew what was going to happen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We knew there was an invasion going on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were told that, but they didn't tell exactly where we'd land.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think it was on the 5th of June we were told that we're going to land on what they called Sword Beach, which was Arromanches.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But that was the only time we really knew where we were going to land on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, this-- it was not a boat, it was a landing ship tank that carried tanks, carried mechanical equipment, carried heavy equipment.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I imagine it could have been, maybe, more than 1,000 soldiers in an LST.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I never counted, obviously.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you just slept on the decks-- there was nowhere to sleep-- and in the lower hold.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they gave what they called field rations.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
